Hello Wako,
&nbsp;
We have enabled the Auto Order Updates feature in the app on your store.
&nbsp;
For your earlier query, unfortunately, preserving the Packing Summary across order updates is not currently supported. When an order is updated in Shopify and the app refreshes its data, the packaging is recalculated from scratch, and any manual parcel assignments you have made are reset. There is no setting at this time to lock or retain custom box assignments when an order syncs.
&nbsp;
One thing worth being aware of: with the Auto Order Update feature being activated for your store, order changes from Shopify will sync to the app automatically. This will solve the order total discrepancy issue going forward, but it does mean the Packing Summary will refresh automatically whenever an order is edited in Shopify.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
However, if your team is updating the Packing Summary after making the necessary updates in Shopify, then you should not face this case again as order once updated in Shopify will be updated in the app as well.
&nbsp;
Please test it with a new order and let us know how it goes.
&nbsp;
Thanks &amp; Regards,
Touseef
Team PluginHive

